@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Rock - Paper - Scissors</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        In a game of rock-paper-scissors, each player chooses to play Rock (R), Paper (P), or Scissors (S). The rules
        are: Rock beats Scissors, Scissors beats Paper, but Paper beats Rock. A Rock-paper-scissors game is encoded as
        a list,where the elements are 2-element lists that encode a player's name and a player's strategy.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Championship</h2>
        <p>
            Process the input data and returns who wins and his strategy.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Top</h2>
        <p>
            Here you can find the winners ordered by their accumulated points.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Samples</h2>
        <p>
            You can easily download examples of the input data.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>